lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich will take a slender lead into the second leg of their Champions League quarter-final against Benfica after Arturo Vidal's early goal earned a 1-0 win over the resolute Portuguese side on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Bayern Edge Resolute Benfica With Early Vidal Goal
